==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: handrail
<hw>hand"rail`</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a rail{1} at the side of
staircase or balcony to prevent people from falling; -- shaped so as to
be conveniently gripped with the hand; <as>as, please hold onto the
<ex>handrail</ex> when crossing the walkway</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> bannister, banister, balustrade,
balusters.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

